msgid "Fit Indices"
msgstr "配適指標"

msgid ""
"Detailed model fit indices. Includes incremental fit indices (CFI, TLI, NFI) "
"comparing the model to the independence model, parsimony-adjusted indices, "
"the RMSEA with confidence interval and close-fit test, SRMR, and information "
"criteria (AIC, BIC, log-likelihood). CFI and TLI values above 0.95, RMSEA "
"below 0.06, and SRMR below 0.08 suggest good fit."
msgstr ""
"詳細模型適配指標。包含比較模型與獨立模型之增量適配指標（CFI、TLI、NFI）、簡效"
"適配指標、RMSEA 及其信賴區間與適配良好性檢定、SRMR，以及資訊準則（AIC、BIC、"
"對數概似）。CFI 與 TLI 值高於 0.95、RMSEA 低於 0.06、SRMR 低於 0.08 表示適配"
"良好。"

msgid "Index"
msgstr "指標"

msgid "Value"
msgstr "值"

msgid "Comparative Fit Index (CFI)"
msgstr "比較配適指標 (CFI)"

msgid "Tucker-Lewis Index (TLI)"
msgstr "Tucker-Lewis 配適指標 (TLI)"

msgid "Bentler-Bonett Non-normed Fit Index (NNFI)"
msgstr "非規範配適指標 (NNFI)"

msgid "Bentler-Bonett Normed Fit Index (NFI)"
msgstr "規範配適指標 (NFI)"

msgid "Parsimony Normed Fit Index (PNFI)"
msgstr "精簡規範配適指標 (PNFI)"

msgid "Bollen's Relative Fit Index (RFI)"
msgstr "相對配適指標 (RFI)"

msgid "Bollen's Incremental Fit Index (IFI)"
msgstr "Bollen's 增量配適指標 (IFI)"

msgid "Relative Noncentrality Index (RNI)"
msgstr "相對非中心性配適指標 (RNI)"

msgid "Root mean square error of approximation (RMSEA)"
msgstr "近似均方根誤差 (RMSEA)"

msgid "RMSEA 90%% CI lower bound"
msgstr "RMSEA 90%% 信賴區間下界"

msgid "RMSEA 90%% CI upper bound"
msgstr "RMSEA 90%% 信賴區間上界"

msgid "RMSEA p-value"
msgstr "RMSEA p值"

msgid "Standardized root mean square residual (SRMR)"
msgstr "標準化殘差均方根 (SRMR)"

msgid "Hoelter's critical N (%s = .05)"
msgstr "Hoelter 臨界樣本數(CN) (%s = .05)"

msgid "Hoelter's critical N (%s = .01)"
msgstr "Hoelter 臨界樣本數(CN) (%s = .01)"

msgid "Goodness of fit index (GFI)"
msgstr "配適度指標 (GFI)"

msgid "McDonald fit index (MFI)"
msgstr "McDonald 配適指標 (MFI)"

msgid "Expected cross validation index (ECVI)"
msgstr "期望交叉驗證指標 (EVCI)"

msgid "Log-likelihood"
msgstr "對數概似"

msgid "Number of free parameters"
msgstr "自由估計參數個數"

msgid "Akaike (AIC)"
msgstr "赤池資訊量準則 (AIC)"

msgid "Bayesian (BIC)"
msgstr "貝氏資訊量準則 (BIC)"

msgid "Sample-size adjusted Bayesian (SSABIC)"
msgstr "依照樣本大小校正之貝氏資訊量準則 (SSABIC)"

msgid "# Factors"
msgstr "# 因素"

msgid ""
"Robust standard errors are not available for variance-covariance matrix "
"input."
msgstr "資料個數少於變數個數，您是以變異數-共變數矩陣為資料進行分析嗎？"

msgid "The model could not be estimated due to nonconvergence."
msgstr "此模型無法估計: 迭代結果無法收斂。"

msgid "The model could not be estimated: No degrees of freedom left."
msgstr "此模型無法估計: 自由度不足。"

msgid "Chi-Square Test"
msgstr "卡方檢定"

msgid ""
"Chi-square goodness-of-fit test comparing the growth curve model to the "
"baseline (independence) model. A non-significant p-value for the growth "
"curve model suggests adequate fit to the data."
msgstr ""
"卡方適配度檢定，用於比較成長曲線模型與基準（獨立）模型。若成長曲線模型之 p 值"
"未達顯著，表示模型與資料適配良好。"

msgid "Model"
msgstr "模型"

msgid "df"
msgstr "自由度"

msgid "p"
msgstr "p"

msgid "Model Fit"
msgstr "模型配適"

msgid "Model fit statistics for the latent growth curve model."
msgstr "潛在成長曲線模型之模型適配統計量。"

msgid "Baseline model"
msgstr "基準模型"

msgid "Growth curve model"
msgstr "成長曲線模型"

msgid "The model is not admissible: %s"
msgstr "此模型無法執行： %s"

msgid "Warning."
msgstr "警告."

msgid "Parameter Estimates"
msgstr "參數估計值"

msgid ""
"Parameter estimates for the latent growth curve model, including growth "
"factor means, variances, covariances, and regression coefficients."
msgstr "潛在成長曲線模型之參數估計值，包含成長因子平均數、變異數、共變數與迴歸係數。"

msgid "Std. estimate"
msgstr "標準化估計值"

msgid "Estimate"
msgstr "估計值"

msgid "Latent Curve"
msgstr "潛在曲線"

msgid ""
"Means and variances of the latent growth factors (e.g., intercept, slope). "
"The intercept mean represents the average starting level, the slope mean the "
"average rate of change, and their variances reflect individual differences "
"in starting level and change."
msgstr ""
"潛在成長因子（例如截距、斜率）之平均數與變異數。截距平均數代表平均起始水準，"
"斜率平均數代表平均變化率，其變異數則反映起始水準與變化率之個別差異。"

msgid "Component"
msgstr "成分"

msgid "Parameter"
msgstr "參數"

msgid "Std. Error"
msgstr "標準誤"

msgid "z-value"
msgstr "z值"

msgid "Lower"
msgstr "下界"

msgid "%s%% Confidence Interval"
msgstr "%s%% 信賴區間"

msgid "Upper"
msgstr "上界"

msgid "Latent Covariances"
msgstr "潛在共變數"

msgid ""
"Covariances between latent growth factors. For example, a positive intercept-"
"slope covariance indicates that individuals with higher starting values tend "
"to show steeper change over time."
msgstr ""
"潛在成長因子間之共變數。例如，截距與斜率之共變數為正，表示起始值較高之個體，"
"隨時間呈現較陡峭的變化趨勢。"

msgid "Regressions"
msgstr "迴歸"

msgid ""
"Regression coefficients of covariates predicting the latent growth factors. "
"These show how external variables relate to individual differences in "
"initial level and rate of change."
msgstr ""
"共變量預測潛在成長因子之迴歸係數。此處顯示外生變項如何與起始水準及變化率之個"
"別差異相關。"

msgid "Predictor"
msgstr "預測變項"

msgid "Residual Variances"
msgstr "殘差變異數"

msgid ""
"Time-specific residual variances of the observed variables. These represent "
"measurement error plus occasion-specific variance not captured by the growth "
"factors. Negative values may indicate model misspecification."
msgstr ""
"觀察變項在特定時間點之殘差變異數。此代表測量誤差加上未被成長因子捕捉之特定時"
"間點變異。若出現負值，可能表示模型設定有誤。"

msgid "Variable"
msgstr "變項"

msgid "Intercept"
msgstr "截距"

msgid "Linear slope"
msgstr "線性斜率"

msgid "Quadratic slope"
msgstr "二次斜率"

msgid "Cubic slope"
msgstr "三次斜率"

msgid "Mean"
msgstr "平均數"

msgid "Variance"
msgstr "變異數"

msgid ""
"Residual variance is negative. This may indicate model misspecification."
msgstr "殘差變異數為負值,此模型可能設定有誤."

msgid "R-Squared"
msgstr "R平方"

msgid ""
"Proportion of variance in each observed variable at each time point "
"explained by the latent growth factors."
msgstr "每個時間點上，各觀察變項之變異數能被潛在成長因子解釋的比例。"

msgid "Implied Covariance Matrix"
msgstr "模式隱含之共變數矩陣"

msgid "Model-implied covariance matrix from the latent growth curve model."
msgstr "潛在成長曲線模型之模型隱含共變數矩陣。"

msgid "Residual Covariance Matrix"
msgstr "殘差共變數矩陣"

msgid ""
"Difference between the observed and model-implied covariance matrices. Small "
"residuals indicate the growth curve model adequately reproduces the observed "
"covariances."
msgstr ""
"觀察共變數矩陣與模型隱含共變數矩陣之差異。殘差較小表示成長曲線模型能夠適當地"
"再現觀察共變數。"

msgid "Curve Plot"
msgstr "曲線圖"

msgid ""
"Individual predicted growth trajectories over time. Each line represents a "
"participant's estimated trajectory based on the latent growth factors."
msgstr "個別預測之隨時間成長軌跡。每一條線代表一位參與者基於潛在成長因子之估計軌跡。"

msgid "Model Plot"
msgstr "模型圖"

msgid ""
"Path diagram of the latent growth curve model showing the growth factors, "
"their loadings on observed time points, and any covariates."
msgstr ""
"潛在成長曲線模型之路徑圖，顯示成長因子、其在各觀察時間點之負荷量，以及任何共"
"變量。"

msgid "Model Syntax"
msgstr "模型的 Lavaan 程式碼"

msgid ""
"The lavaan model syntax for the growth curve model, showing fixed factor "
"loadings that define the growth trajectory shape."
msgstr "潛在成長曲線模型之 lavaan 模型語法，顯示定義成長軌跡形狀之固定因素負荷量。"

msgid "Misfit Plot"
msgstr "不適配 (misfit) 圖"

msgid "Curve + variance + uncertainty"
msgstr "曲線 + 變異數 + 不確定性"

msgid "Curve + variance"
msgstr "曲線 + 變異數"

msgid "Curve + parameter uncertainty"
msgstr "曲線 + 參數不確定性"

msgid ""
"Not all exogenous variables are admissible. Inadmissible exogenous "
"variables: %s. Only binary or continuous exogenous variables allowed."
msgstr "並非所有外生變數都有合理解，如：%s。只能使用二元或連續外生變數。"

msgid ""
"Not all endogenous variables are admissible. Inadmissible endogenous "
"variables: %s. Only scale or ordinal endogenous variables allowed."
msgstr "並非所有內生變數都有合理解，如：%s。只能使用連續或次序內生變數。"

msgid ""
"FIML missing value handling only available when all endogenous variables are "
"of scale type. Ordinal endogenous variables in the model: %s"
msgstr ""
"只能在所有內生變數皆為連續變數時，才能使用完全訊息最大概似法遺漏值處理設定。"
"模型中有以下次序內生變數：%s"

msgid ""
"Estimation failed\n"
"Message:\n"
"%s"
msgstr ""
"無法估計\n"
"訊息:\n"
"%s"

msgid "Estimation failed"
msgstr "估計失敗"

msgid ""
"Parameter estimates from the mediation model, organized by direct effects, "
"indirect effects, and total effects."
msgstr "中介模型之參數估計值，按直接效果、間接效果與總效果彙整呈現。"

msgid "Direct effects"
msgstr "直接效果"

msgid ""
"Direct effects of predictors on outcomes, bypassing all mediators (the c or "
"c' path). A significant direct effect indicates that the predictor "
"influences the outcome independently of the mediation pathway."
msgstr ""
"預測變項對結果變項之直接效果，未經過任何中介變項（c 或 c' 路徑）。若直接效果"
"顯著，表示預測變項在不經由中介路徑的情況下，仍對結果變項有影響。"

msgid "Indirect effects"
msgstr "間接效果"

msgid ""
"Indirect effects of predictors on outcomes transmitted through mediators. "
"Each indirect effect is the product of the path coefficients along the "
"mediation pathway (a × b). A significant indirect effect indicates that "
"mediation occurs through that pathway."
msgstr ""
"預測變項透過中介變項傳遞至結果變項之間接效果。每個間接效果為該中介路徑上路徑"
"係數之乘積（a × b）。若間接效果顯著，表示該路徑確實存在中介效果。"

msgid "Total Effects"
msgstr "總效果"

msgid ""
"Total effects combining the direct effect and all indirect effects for each "
"predictor-outcome pair. The total effect equals the sum of the direct and "
"indirect effects (c = c' + a × b)."
msgstr ""
"總效果，即每個預測變項－結果變項配對之直接效果與所有間接效果之總和。總效果等"
"於直接效果與間接效果之和（c = c' + a × b）。"

msgid "Total indirect effects"
msgstr "所有間接效果"

msgid ""
"Total indirect effects summed across all mediators for each predictor-"
"outcome pair. When there are multiple mediators, this gives the combined "
"strength of all indirect pathways."
msgstr ""
"總間接效果，即每個預測變項－結果變項配對中，所有中介變項之間接效果總和。當存"
"在多個中介變項時，此值代表所有間接路徑之合併效果量。"

msgid "Residual covariances"
msgstr "殘差共變數"

msgid ""
"Estimated residual covariances between endogenous variables (mediators and "
"outcomes). These represent shared variance not accounted for by the model's "
"directed paths."
msgstr ""
"內生變項（中介變項與結果變項）間之估計殘差共變數。此代表未被模型中直接路徑所"
"解釋的共同變異。"

msgid "Path coefficients"
msgstr "路徑係數"

msgid ""
"Individual path coefficients in the mediation model. These include the a "
"paths (predictor to mediator) and b paths (mediator to outcome), which "
"constitute the building blocks of indirect effects."
msgstr ""
"中介模型中之個別路徑係數。此包含 a 路徑（預測變項對中介變項）與 b 路徑（中介"
"變項對結果變項），兩者為構成間接效果之基本元素。"

msgid "Estimator is %s."
msgstr "估計法為 %s。"

msgid ""
"%1$s Not all bootstrap samples were successful: CI based on %2$.0f samples."
msgstr ""
"%1$s 並非所有拔靴法樣本皆分析成功: 信賴區間是基於 %2$.0f 的樣本分析結果。"

msgid ""
"Proportion of variance in each mediator and outcome variable explained by "
"its predictors in the mediation model."
msgstr "中介模型中，每個中介變項與結果變項能被其預測變項所解釋的變異比例。"

msgid "Path Plot"
msgstr "路徑圖"

msgid ""
"Visual representation of the mediation model showing predictors, mediators, "
"outcomes, directed paths, and (optionally) parameter estimates."
msgstr ""
"中介模型之視覺化呈現，顯示預測變項、中介變項、結果變項、直接路徑，以及（選擇"
"性）參數估計值。"

msgid ""
"Currently it is not possible to plot mediation models with ordinal "
"variables. The plot could not be generated."
msgstr "因包含次序變數而無法繪製中介模型圖，無法產生圖形。"

msgid ""
"The plot could not be generated. The underlying code resulted in the "
"following error message: %s"
msgstr "無法產生圖形。錯誤訊息後所列之語法有誤: %s"

msgid "Model syntax"
msgstr "模型的 Lavaan 程式碼"

msgid ""
"The lavaan model syntax automatically generated from the mediation analysis "
"specification. This shows the exact model fitted, including labeled direct "
"and indirect effect parameters."
msgstr ""
"根據中介分析規格自動生成之 lavaan 模型語法。此處顯示實際配適之模型，包含已標"
"示之直接效果與間接效果參數。"

msgid "FIML only available with ML-type estimators."
msgstr "只有使用最大概似法 (ML)類估計法時才提供完全訊息最大概似法(FIML)功能。"

msgid ""
"Estimation failed! Message: The model did not converge. Try using a "
"different estimator or specify an other MIMIC model."
msgstr "估計失敗！訊息：模型無法收斂。試使用其他估計法，或改用其他MIMIC模型。"

msgid ""
"Chi-square goodness-of-fit test for the MIMIC model. Both the baseline "
"(independence) model and the factor model with predictors are shown. A non-"
"significant chi-square for the factor model indicates adequate fit."
msgstr ""
"MIMIC 模型之卡方適配度檢定。表中同時呈現基準（獨立）模型與納入預測變項之因素"
"模型。若因素模型之卡方值未達顯著，表示模型適配良好。"

msgid "&#967;&sup2;"
msgstr "&#967;&sup2;"

msgid "Factor model"
msgstr "因素模型"

msgid ""
"Parameter estimates for the MIMIC (Multiple Indicators, Multiple Causes) "
"model. The model has observed predictors influencing a latent variable, "
"which in turn is measured by observed indicators."
msgstr ""
"MIMIC（多指標多原因）模型之參數估計值。該模型由觀察預測變項影響潛在變項，潛在"
"變項再進一步由觀察指標所測量。"

msgid "Predictor coefficients"
msgstr "預測變數係數"

msgid ""
"Regression coefficients of the observed predictor (cause) variables on the "
"latent variable. These represent the direct effects of each predictor on the "
"latent construct."
msgstr ""
"觀察預測變項（原因）對潛在變項之迴歸係數。此代表每個預測變項對潛在構念之直接"
"效果。"

msgid "Indicator coefficients"
msgstr "指標係數"

msgid ""
"Factor loadings of the latent variable on its observed indicators. These "
"represent how strongly each indicator reflects the underlying latent "
"construct."
msgstr "潛在變項對其觀察指標之因素負荷量。此代表每個指標反映潛在構念之強度。"

msgid "Indicator"
msgstr "指標"

msgid ""
"Proportion of variance explained in the latent variable (by the predictors) "
"and in each indicator (by the latent variable)."
msgstr "潛在變項被預測變項解釋之變異比例，以及每個觀察指標被潛在變項解釋之變異比例。"

msgid ""
"Path diagram of the MIMIC model showing observed predictors (causes), the "
"latent variable, and its observed indicators."
msgstr "MIMIC 模型之路徑圖，顯示觀察預測變項（原因）、潛在變項，以及其觀察指標。"

msgid "Model plot not available with ordinal variables"
msgstr "使用次序變數分析時，無法提供模型圖"

msgid ""
"The lavaan model syntax specifying the MIMIC model structure, including the "
"measurement model and the regression of the latent variable on the "
"predictors."
msgstr ""
"指定 MIMIC 模型結構之 lavaan 模型語法，包含測量模型以及潛在變項對預測變項之迴"
"歸。"

msgid ""
"Specify both factor indicator variables and moderator variables to run the "
"analysis."
msgstr "請同時指定因子指標變數與調節變數以執行分析。"

msgid "Check the 'Sync Analysis' box to run the analysis."
msgstr "勾選「同步分析」方塊以執行分析。"

msgid ""
"The moderator variable '%s' already has '_squared' in its name. Please "
"rename the variable before proceeding."
msgstr "調節變數「%s」的名稱中已包含「_squared」。請在繼續之前重新命名該變數。"

msgid ""
"The moderator variable '%s' already has '_cubic' in its name. Please rename "
"the variable before proceeding."
msgstr "調節變數「%s」的名稱中已包含「_cubic」。請在繼續之前重新命名該變數。"

msgid "Fitting invariance model"
msgstr "擬合不變性模型"

msgid "Fit per Group Test"
msgstr "分組擬合檢定"

msgid ""
"CFA fit statistics computed separately for each group defined by the "
"moderator. This checks whether the baseline factor model fits adequately "
"within each group before testing invariance."
msgstr ""
"針對調節變項所定義之各群組分別計算的 CFA 適配統計量。此用於在檢驗不變性之前，"
"確認基準因素模型在各群組內是否適配良好。"

msgid "Group Model"
msgstr "分組模型"

msgid "Error in fit per group test. Internal error message(s): %s"
msgstr "分組擬合檢定時發生錯誤。內部錯誤訊息：%s"

msgid "N"
msgstr ""

msgid "RMSEA"
msgstr "RMSEA"

msgid "CFI"
msgstr "CFI"

msgid "SRMR"
msgstr ""

msgid "The model for group %s did not converge."
msgstr "群組 %s 的模型未收斂。"

msgid "Global Invariance Fit"
msgstr "整體不變性擬合"

msgid ""
"Comparison of MNLFA invariance models (configural, metric, scalar, strict) "
"using -2 log-likelihood difference tests. Significant differences indicate "
"that the more constrained model fits significantly worse, suggesting non-"
"invariance at that level."
msgstr ""
"使用 -2 對數概似差異檢定比較 MNLFA 不變性模型（組態、度量、純量、嚴格）。若差"
"異顯著，表示限制較多之模型適配顯著較差，顯示該層級存在不變性違反。"

msgid "Type"
msgstr "類型"

#, fuzzy
msgid "n(Par)"
msgstr "參數個數"

msgid "Fit (-2LL)"
msgstr "擬合 (-2LL)"

msgid "AIC"
msgstr "AIC"

msgid "SAAIC"
msgstr ""

msgid "BIC"
msgstr "BIC"

msgid "SABIC"
msgstr ""

msgid "Choose one of the global invariance tests to perform the test."
msgstr "請選擇其中一個整體不變性檢定來執行檢驗。"

msgid "Δ(LL)"
msgstr ""

