msgstr ""

msgid "%1$s Error in fitting the %2$s model. Internal error message(s): %3$s"
msgstr "擬合 %2$s 模型時發生 %1$s 錯誤。內部錯誤訊息：%3$s"

msgid "OK"
msgstr ""

msgid "%1$s: optimizer status '%2$s'."
msgstr "%1$s：最佳化器狀態 '%2$s'。"

msgid ""
"Fitting the model resulted in warnings. Check the 'Show warnings' box in the "
"Output Options to see the warnings."
msgstr "配適模型時產生警告。請勾選「輸出選項」中的「顯示警告」以查看警告內容。"

msgid "Warnings (from R):"
msgstr "警告（來自 R）："

msgid ""
"Parameter estimates from the MNLFA invariance models. Moderation effects "
"show how each parameter varies as a function of the moderator variable. "
"Estimates on 'Effect' rows represent the linear change in the parameter per "
"unit change in the moderator."
msgstr ""
"MNLFA 不變性模型之參數估計值。調節效果顯示各參數如何隨調節變項變化。在「效果"
"」列之估計值代表調節變項每改變一個單位，該參數之線性變化量。"

msgid "The %s model could not be fitted"
msgstr "無法擬合 %s 模型"

msgid "Loadings"
msgstr "因素負荷量"

msgid ""
"Factor loadings and their moderation effects. Significant moderation effects "
"indicate that the relationship between the latent factor and its indicator "
"varies across levels of the moderator (metric non-invariance)."
msgstr ""
"因素負荷量及其調節效果。若調節效果顯著，表示潛在因素與其指標之間的關係會隨調"
"節變項之水準而變化（度量不變性違反）。"

msgid "Factor"
msgstr "因子"

msgid "Effect"
msgstr "效果"

msgid "Intercepts"
msgstr "截距"

msgid ""
"Indicator intercepts and their moderation effects. Significant moderation "
"effects indicate that the item difficulty or baseline level varies across "
"the moderator (scalar non-invariance)."
msgstr ""
"指標截距及其調節效果。若調節效果顯著，表示試題難度或基準水準會隨調節變項而變"
"化（純量不變性違反）。"

msgid ""
"Indicator residual variances and their moderation effects. Estimates are on "
"the log scale internally and back-transformed for display. Significant "
"moderation indicates that measurement precision varies across the moderator "
"(strict non-invariance)."
msgstr ""
"指標殘差變異數及其調節效果。估計值內部採對數尺度，顯示時已反轉換。若調節效果"
"顯著，表示測量精確度會隨調節變項而變化（違反嚴格不變性）。"

msgid "Factor Variances"
msgstr "因素變異數"

msgid ""
"Latent factor variances and their moderation effects. Estimates are on the "
"log scale internally and back-transformed for display. Significant "
"moderation indicates that the spread of the latent trait changes across the "
"moderator."
msgstr ""
"潛在因素變異數及其調節效果。估計值內部採對數尺度，顯示時已反轉換。若調節效果"
"顯著，表示潛在特質之離散程度會隨調節變項而變化。"

msgid "Factor Means"
msgstr "因素平均數"

msgid ""
"Latent factor means and their moderation effects. Significant moderation "
"indicates that the average level of the latent trait differs across the "
"moderator."
msgstr ""
"潛在因素平均數及其調節效果。若調節效果顯著，表示潛在特質之平均水準會隨調節變"
"項而不同。"

msgid "Factor Covariances"
msgstr "因素共變數"

msgid ""
"Latent factor covariances and their moderation effects. Significant "
"moderation indicates that the relationship between latent factors varies "
"across the moderator."
msgstr ""
"潛在因素共變數及其調節效果。若調節效果顯著，表示潛在因素之間的關係會隨調節變"
"項而變化。"

msgid "Parameter Plots"
msgstr "參數圖"

msgid ""
"Plots showing how model parameters (loadings, intercepts, variances) vary as "
"a function of the moderator variable. Each plot displays the estimated "
"parameter value across the range of the moderator."
msgstr ""
"模型參數（負荷量、截距、變異數）隨調節變項變化之圖形。每個圖形顯示參數估計值"
"在調節變項整個範圍內之變化情形。"

msgid "total"
msgstr "總計"

msgid "Parameter Value"
msgstr "參數值"

msgid "Nothing to print."
msgstr "沒有可列印的內容。"

msgid "addedGroupVariable"
msgstr "已新增的群組變數"

msgid "Column name %s already exists in the dataset"
msgstr "資料集中已存在欄位名稱 %s"

msgid "# LOADINGS BLOCK"
msgstr "# 負荷量區塊"

msgid "Baseline"
msgstr "基準線"

msgid "# FACTOR VARIANCES BLOCK"
msgstr "# 因子變異數區塊"

msgid "# FACTOR MEANS BLOCK"
msgstr "# 因子平均數區塊"

msgid "# INTERCEPTS BLOCK"
msgstr "# 截距區塊"

msgid "# RESIDUAL VARIANCES BLOCK"
msgstr "# 殘差變異數區塊"

msgid "# FACTOR COVARIANCES BLOCK"
msgstr "# 因素共變異數區塊"

msgid "Error"
msgstr "錯誤"

msgid "Unknown"
msgstr "未知"

msgid "OK/Gradient"
msgstr ""

msgid "Non-convex Hessian"
msgstr "非凸 Hessian 矩陣"

msgid "Unchecked"
msgstr "未勾選"

msgid "Code %s"
msgstr ""

msgid "Grouping variable has fewer than 3 observations in group %s"
msgstr "分組變數在%s組中的觀察值小於3"

msgid "Enter a model"
msgstr "輸入模型"

msgid "Variable(s) in model syntax not recognized: %s"
msgstr "模型語法中的變數無法辨識：%s"

msgid "Using '~~' is not supported for composite covariances. Try '~' instead"
msgstr "不支援使用「~~」來設定組合變數的共變異數。請改用「~」"

msgid "Using '~~' is not supported. Try '~' instead"
msgstr "不支援使用「~~」。請改用「~」"

msgid "Estimation failed Message: %s"
msgstr "估計失敗。訊息:%s"

msgid "Estimation failed! Message: Model %s did not converge!"
msgstr "估計失敗。訊息:模型%s無法收斂!"

msgid ""
"Overall model fit test using bootstrap-based distance measures. The test "
"statistic is compared to a critical value obtained from bootstrapping. If "
"the test statistic exceeds the critical value, the model is rejected at the "
"chosen significance level."
msgstr ""
"使用基於拔靴法之距離指標進行的整體模型適配度檢定。檢定統計量與從拔靴法所得之"
"臨界值進行比較。若檢定統計量超過臨界值，則在選定之顯著水準下拒絕該模型。"

msgid "Group"
msgstr "組別"

msgid "Distance Measure"
msgstr "距離測量"

msgid "Test Statistic"
msgstr "檢定統計量"

msgid "Critical Value (%s%% Quantile)"
msgstr "臨界值（%s%% 分位數）"

msgid "Model selection criteria could not be computed: %s"
msgstr "無法計算模型選擇準則：%s"

msgid "Model selection criteria could not be computed for group %1$s: %2$s"
msgstr "無法計算群組 %1$s 的模型選擇準則：%2$s"

msgid "At least one result is inadmissible."
msgstr "至少有一個結果不可採用。"

msgid "Denotes the fit of the model including a saturated structural model."
msgstr "表示包含飽和結構模型的模型擬合度。"

msgid ""
"Parameter estimates for the PLS-SEM model, including outer weights, outer "
"loadings, inner model path coefficients, total effects, and residual "
"correlations."
msgstr ""
"PLS-SEM 模型之參數估計值，包含外部權重、外部負荷量、內部模型路徑係數、總效果"
"與殘差相關。"

msgid "Weights"
msgstr "加權"

msgid ""
"Outer weights relating observed indicators to their composite constructs. "
"Weights determine how indicators are combined to form construct scores and "
"reflect each indicator's relative contribution."
msgstr ""
"觀察指標與其組合型構念間之關係的外部權重。權重決定指標如何組合成構念分數，並"
"反映每個指標之相對貢獻。"

msgid "Construct"
msgstr "構念"

msgid ""
"Outer loadings (correlations) between indicators and their constructs. "
"Loadings above 0.708 indicate that the construct explains more than 50%% of "
"the indicator's variance."
msgstr ""
"指標與其構念間之相關（外部負荷量）。負荷量大於 0.708 表示該構念能解釋指標超"
"過 50% 的變異量。"

msgid "Regression Coefficients"
msgstr "迴歸係數"

msgid ""
"Inner model path coefficients between constructs. The f² effect size "
"indicates the substantive impact of removing each predictor: 0.02 (small), "
"0.15 (medium), 0.35 (large)."
msgstr ""
"構念之間內部模型之路徑係數。f² 效果量代表移除每個預測變項之實質影響：0.02（小"
"）、0.15（中）、0.35（大）。"

msgid "Outcome"
msgstr "結果"

msgid ""
"Total effects combining direct and all indirect paths between constructs."
msgstr "結合構念之間直接路徑與所有間接路徑之總效果。"

msgid "Residual Correlations"
msgstr "殘差相關"

msgid ""
"Residual correlations between indicators after accounting for the construct "
"model. These represent correlated measurement errors between indicator pairs."
msgstr "考量構念模型後，指標間之殘差相關。此代表成對指標之間的相關測量誤差。"

msgid "VIF"
msgstr "VIF"

msgid "VIF could not be computed."
msgstr "無法計算 VIF。"

msgid "Endogenous Indicator Prediction"
msgstr "內衍指標預測"

msgid ""
"Cross-validated prediction of endogenous indicators using PLSpredict. The "
"prediction metrics assess how well the PLS-SEM model predicts indicator "
"scores out of sample."
msgstr ""
"使用 PLSpredict 對內生指標進行交叉驗證預測。預測指標用於評估 PLS-SEM 模型在樣"
"本外預測指標分數之表現。"

msgid "Prediction Metrics"
msgstr "預測指標"

msgid ""
"MAE (mean absolute error), RMSE (root mean squared error), and Q² prediction "
"metrics for endogenous indicators. Q² > 0 indicates that prediction error is "
"less than using the training sample mean. When benchmarks are included, "
"lower MAE/RMSE than the benchmark suggests the PLS-SEM model predicts better."
msgstr ""
"內生指標之 MAE（平均絕對誤差）、RMSE（均方根誤差）與 Q² 預測指標。Q² > 0 表示"
"預測誤差小於使用訓練樣本平均數之誤差。若包含基準模型，當 MAE / RMSE 低於基準"
"模型時，表示 PLS-SEM 模型之預測表現較佳。"

msgid "Target MAE"
msgstr "目標 MAE"

msgid "LM MAE"
msgstr ""

msgid "GSCA MAE"
msgstr ""

msgid "PCA MAE"
msgstr ""

msgid "MAXVAR MAE"
msgstr ""

msgid "Target RMSE"
msgstr "目標 RMSE"

msgid "LM RMSE"
msgstr ""

msgid "GSCA RMSE"
msgstr ""

msgid "PCA RMSE"
msgstr ""

msgid "MAXVAR RMSE"
msgstr ""

msgid "Target Q2 Prediction"
msgstr "目標 Q2 預測"

msgid ""
"There are not enough observations for each k-fold, try setting 'cross-"
"validation k-folds' to a lower number"
msgstr "每個 k 折的觀察值數量不足，請嘗試將「交叉驗證 k 折數」設為較小的數值"

msgid "Are all indicator variables set to 'scale'?"
msgstr "所有指標變數是否皆設定為連續變數？"

msgid "Prediction failed Message: %1$s"
msgstr "估計失敗。訊息:%s"

msgid "Additional Fit Measures"
msgstr "其他配適指標"

msgid ""
"Additional model fit measures for PLS-SEM. Includes CFI, GFI, RMSEA, SRMR "
"for the model-implied indicator correlation matrix, Goodness-of-Fit (GoF) as "
"geometric mean of AVE and R², and bootstrap-based distance measures (dG, dL, "
"dML)."
msgstr ""
"PLS-SEM 之額外模型適配指標。包含模型隱含指標相關矩陣之 CFI、GFI、RMSEA、SRMR"
"，平均變異萃取量（AVE）與 R² 之幾何平均（GoF），以及基於拔靴法之距離指標（dG"
"、dL、dML）。"

msgid "Hoelter's critical N (CN)"
msgstr "Hoelter 臨界樣本數 (CN)"

msgid "Root mean square residual covariance (RMS theta)"
msgstr "均方根殘差共變數 (RMS theta)"

msgid "Goodness of Fit (GoF)"
msgstr "配適度指標 (GFI)"

msgid "Geodesic distance"
msgstr "測地距離"

msgid "Squared Euclidean distance"
msgstr "平方歐式距離"

msgid "Maximum likelihood-based distance"
msgstr "基於最大概似法之距離"

msgid "Model assessment could not be computed: %s"
msgstr "無法計算模型評估：%s"

msgid "Model assessment could not be computed for group %1$s: %2$s"
msgstr "無法計算群組 %1$s 的模型評估：%2$s"

msgid ""
"R² and adjusted R² for each endogenous construct. R² represents the "
"proportion of variance in the construct explained by its predictors in the "
"structural model. Values of 0.75, 0.50, and 0.25 are considered substantial, "
"moderate, and weak."
msgstr ""
"每個內生構念之 R² 與調整後 R²。R² 代表結構模型中該構念能被其預測變項解釋之變"
"異比例。0.75、0.50 與 0.25 分別視為高、中、低程度。"

msgid "R²"
msgstr ""

msgid "Adjusted R²"
msgstr "調整後 R²"

msgid "Reliability Measures"
msgstr "信度指標 (Cronbach's α 與 CR值)"

msgid ""
"Construct reliability measures. Cronbach's α assumes equal indicator weights "
"(tau-equivalence). Jöreskog's ρ uses the outer loadings and is the preferred "
"measure for PLS-SEM. Dijkstra-Henseler's ρ_A is a consistent reliability "
"estimate. Values above 0.70 indicate acceptable reliability."
msgstr ""
"構念信度指標。Cronbach's α 假設指標權重相等（tau-等效性）。Jöreskog's ρ 使用"
"外部負荷量，為 PLS-SEM 較常採用之信度指標。Dijkstra-Henseler's ρ_A 為一致之信"
"度估計值。數值高於 0.70 表示信度可接受。"

msgid "Latent"
msgstr "潛在"

msgid "Cronbach's %s"
msgstr "Cronbach %s"

msgid "J%1$sreskog's %2$s"
msgstr ""

msgid "Dijkstra-Henseler's %s"
msgstr ""

msgid "Correlation Tables"
msgstr "相關係數表"

msgid ""
"Observed and model-implied correlation matrices for indicators and "
"constructs. Comparing observed and implied matrices helps assess model fit "
"at the indicator and construct level."
msgstr ""
"指標與構念之觀察相關矩陣與模型隱含相關矩陣。比較觀察與隱含矩陣有助於評估模型"
"在指標與構念層次之適配度。"

msgid "Observed Indicator Correlation Matrix"
msgstr "觀察指標相關矩陣"

msgid "Sample correlation matrix of the observed indicator variables."
msgstr "觀察指標變項之樣本相關矩陣。"

msgid "Implied Indicator Correlation Matrix"
msgstr "隱含指標相關矩陣"

msgid ""
"Model-implied correlation matrix of the indicator variables. Closeness to "
"the observed matrix indicates good model fit at the indicator level."
msgstr ""
"模型隱含之指標變項相關矩陣。此矩陣與觀察矩陣愈接近，表示模型在指標層次之適配"
"度愈好。"

msgid "Observed Construct Correlation Matrix"
msgstr "觀察構念相關矩陣"

msgid "Sample correlation matrix of the composite construct scores."
msgstr "組合構念分數之樣本相關矩陣。"

msgid "Implied Construct Correlation Matrix"
msgstr "隱含構念相關矩陣"

msgid ""
"Model-implied correlation matrix of the constructs. Closeness to the "
"observed construct correlations indicates good structural model fit."
msgstr ""
"模型隱含之構念相關矩陣。此矩陣與觀察構念相關愈接近，表示結構模型之適配度愈好"
"。"

msgid ""
"Sample correlation matrix of the observed indicator variables, shown per "
"group."
msgstr "各群組之觀察指標變項樣本相關矩陣。"

msgid ""
"Model-implied correlation matrix of the indicator variables, shown per group."
msgstr "各群組之模型隱含指標變項相關矩陣。"

msgid ""
"Sample correlation matrix of the composite construct scores, shown per group."
msgstr "各群組之組合構念分數樣本相關矩陣。"

msgid "Model-implied correlation matrix of the constructs, shown per group."
msgstr "各群組之模型隱含構念相關矩陣。"

msgid "Implied indicator correlations could not be computed: %s"
msgstr "無法計算隱含指標相關性：%s"

msgid "Implied construct correlations could not be computed: %s"
msgstr "無法計算隱含構念相關性：%s"

msgid ""
"Mean structure can not be included when data is variance-covariance matrix"
msgstr "當以變異數-共變數矩陣為資料進行分析時，無法提供平均數結構"

msgid "Please set the sample size!"
msgstr "請設定樣本數!"

msgid ""
"Multiple group analysis not supported when data is variance-covariance matrix"
msgstr "當以變異數-共變數矩陣為資料進行分析時，無法進行多群分析"

msgid ""
"Not more cases than number of variables. Is your data a variance-covariance "
"matrix?"
msgstr "資料個數少於變項個數，你是以變異數-共變數矩陣為資料進行分析嗎？"

msgid ""
"When conditioning estimation on exogenous covariates, the 'Exogenous "
"covariate(s) fixed' box must be checked."
msgstr "當條件估計是基於外衍共變數時，必須勾選「固定外衍共變數」。"

msgid ""
"Bootstrapped standard errors are not yet available when 'Condition on "
"exogenous covariate(s)' box is checked."
msgstr "勾選「考量外衍共變數」時，無法提供拔靴法標準誤。"

msgid "Invalid model specification. Did you pass a variable name as a string?"
msgstr "模型設定無效。是否將某變數名稱誤設為字串資料？"

msgid "One or more variables are constants or contain only missing values."
msgstr "一或多個變數為常數或只有遺漏值。"

msgid "Estimation failed. Message: %s"
msgstr "估計失敗。訊息:%s"

msgid "Estimation failed! Message: %s did not converge!"
msgstr "估計失敗。訊息:模型%s無法收斂！"

msgid "Estimation failed! Message: %s has negative degrees of freedom."
msgstr "估計失敗!訊息:模型%s的自由度為負值。"

msgid ""
"Model fit statistics including AIC, BIC, number of parameters, and a chi-"
"square test for exact fit. A non-significant chi-square suggests the model "
"fits the data well, though this test is sensitive to sample size."
msgstr ""
"模型適配統計量，包含 AIC、BIC、參數個數與精確適配卡方檢定。卡方值未達顯著表示"
"模型與資料適配良好，惟該檢定容易受樣本數影響。"

msgid "n(Observations)"
msgstr "樣本數"

msgid "Total"
msgstr "總計"

msgid "n(Parameters)"
msgstr "參數個數"

msgid "Free"
msgstr "自由參數"

msgid "Baseline test"
msgstr "模型檢定"

msgid "Difference test"
msgstr "差異檢定"

msgid "%1$sdf"
msgstr "%1$s自由度"

msgid ""
"%sFitting the model resulted in warnings. Check the 'Show warnings' box in "
"the Output Options to see the warnings."
msgstr "%s擬合模型時出現警告。勾選「輸出選項」中的「顯示警告」以察看警告訊息。"

msgid "A total of %g cases were removed due to missing values."
msgstr "有 %g 筆資料因有遺漏值而未納入分析。"

msgid "Model test is %s."
msgstr "模型考驗為 %s。"

msgid "Information matrix is %s."
msgstr "資訊矩陣為 %s。"

msgid "Standard errors are %s."
msgstr "標準誤為 %s。"

msgid ""
"%s The AIC, BIC and additional information criteria are only available with "
"ML-type estimators."
msgstr ""
"%s 只有在使用最大概似法 (ML)類之估計法時，才提供AIC, BIC與其他訊息準則指標。"

msgid "all"
msgstr "所有參數"

msgid "<b>Warnings:</b> %s"
msgstr "<b>警告:</b> %s"

msgid ""
"Parameter estimates from the structural equation model, organized by type: "
"factor loadings, regression coefficients, variances, covariances, and "
"additional parameters."
msgstr ""
"結構方程模型之參數估計值，按類型彙整：因素負荷量、迴歸係數、變異數、共變數與"
"其他參數。"

msgid "Factor Loadings"
msgstr "因素負荷量"

msgid ""
"Factor loadings from the measurement model (=~ operator). Each loading "
"reflects how strongly a latent variable is related to its observed "
"indicator. The first indicator loading is typically fixed to 1 to set the "
"scale of the latent variable."
msgstr ""
"測量模型之因素負荷量（=~ 運算子）。每個負荷量反映潛在變項與其觀察指標之間關係"
"的強度。第一個指標之負荷量通常固定為 1，以設定潛在變項之量尺。"

msgid ""
"Regression coefficients from the structural part of the model (~ operator). "
"These represent directed effects of predictors on outcomes among latent and/"
"or observed variables."
msgstr ""
"模型結構部分之迴歸係數（~ 運算子）。此代表潛在變項及／或觀察變項之間，預測變"
"項對結果變項之直接效果。"

msgid ""
"Estimated variances of the latent variables. For exogenous latent variables "
"these are total variances; for endogenous latent variables these are "
"residual variances (the variance not explained by predictors)."
msgstr ""
"潛在變項之估計變異數。外生潛在變項為總變異數；內生潛在變項則為殘差變異數（未"
"被預測變項解釋之變異）。"

msgid ""
"Estimated covariances between latent variables (~~ operator). These "
"represent undirected associations between latent variables."
msgstr "潛在變項間之估計共變數（~~ 運算子）。此代表潛在變項之間非定向之關聯性。"

msgid "Variables"
msgstr "變項"

msgid ""
"Residual variances of the observed variables: the variance not explained by "
"the latent variables. Negative residual variances (Heywood cases) may "
"indicate model misspecification."
msgstr ""
"觀察變項之殘差變異數：未被潛在變項解釋之變異。若殘差變異數為負（Heywood 案例"
"），可能表示模型設定有誤。"

msgid "Residual Covariances"
msgstr "殘差共變數"

msgid ""
"Residual covariances between observed variables (~~ operator). These "
"represent correlated errors, i.e., shared variance between indicators not "
"accounted for by the latent variables."
msgstr ""
"觀察變項間之殘差共變數（~~ 運算子）。此代表相關誤差，即未被潛在變項解釋之指標"
"間共同變異。"

msgid ""
"Intercept (mean) parameters for observed and latent variables in the mean "
"structure. For observed variables, these are the expected values when all "
"predictors are zero."
msgstr ""
"平均數結構中觀察變項與潛在變項之截距（平均數）參數。對觀察變項而言，此為所有"
"預測變項為零時之期望值。"

msgid "Missing data method 'FIML' forces meanstructure."
msgstr "缺失資料方法 'FIML' 強制要求均值結構"

msgid "Thresholds"
msgstr "閾限"

msgid ""
"Threshold parameters for ordinal observed variables. These define the cut-"
"points on the underlying continuous distribution that separate the observed "
"categories."
msgstr "次序觀察變項之閾限參數。此定義潛在連續分配上將觀察類別分開之切截點。"

msgid "Threshold"
msgstr "閾限"

msgid "Defined Parameters"
msgstr "定義之參數"

msgid ""
"User-defined parameters specified with the := operator. These are functions "
"of existing model parameters, such as indirect effects or sums of "
"coefficients. Standard errors are computed using the Delta method."
msgstr ""
"使用者透過 := 運算子定義之參數。此為現有模型參數之函數，例如間接效果或係數和"
"。其標準誤使用 Delta 法計算。"

msgid "Name"
msgstr "命名"

msgid "Indirect Effects"
msgstr "間接效果"

msgid ""
"Indirect effects of predictors on outcomes transmitted through mediating "
"variables. These are computed as the product of the path coefficients along "
"the indirect pathway."
msgstr ""
"預測變項透過中介變項傳遞至結果變項之間接效果。此為該間接路徑上路徑係數之乘積"
"。"

msgid ""
"Total effects combining direct and all indirect effects of predictors on "
"outcomes."
msgstr "結合預測變項對結果變項之直接效果與所有間接效果之總效果。"

msgid ""
"Additional model fit indices and information criteria for evaluating overall "
"model quality."
msgstr "用於評估整體模型品質之額外模型適配指標與資訊準則。"

msgid ""
"Model fit indices including incremental indices (CFI, TLI, NFI), absolute "
"indices (RMSEA, SRMR, GFI), and information criteria (AIC, BIC). Common "
"guidelines: CFI/TLI > .95, RMSEA < .06, SRMR < .08 indicate good fit, though "
"these should be interpreted cautiously."
msgstr ""
"模型適配指標包含增量適配指標（CFI、TLI、NFI）、絕對適配指標（RMSEA、SRMR、GFI"
"），以及資訊準則（AIC、BIC）。常見參考標準：CFI / TLI > .95、RMSEA < .06、"
"SRMR < .08 表示適配良好，惟應用時仍須謹慎解讀。"

msgid "%s Fit indices are based on the scaled test statistic."
msgstr "%s 配適指標，將基於量尺化檢定統計數。"

msgid "T-Size Fit Indices"
msgstr "T-size 配適指標"

msgid ""
"T-size equivalence testing fit indices (Marcoulides & Yuan, 2017). These "
"provide data-driven cutoff values for CFI and RMSEA that replace "
"conventional rules of thumb. The poor-fair and fair-close limits define "
"ranges for interpreting fit."
msgstr ""
"T-size 等價性檢定適配指標（Marcoulides & Yuan, 2017）。此指標提供 CFI 與 "
"RMSEA 之資料驅動臨界值，以取代傳統經驗法則。不良－尚可與尚可－良好之界限界定"
"出適配度解讀之範圍。"

msgid "Poor-fair limit"
msgstr "差至可接受臨界值"

msgid "Fair-close limit"
msgstr "可接受至良好臨界值"

msgid "T-size statistics are computed for <i>%s = 0.05</i>."
msgstr "T 值統計量是針對 <i>%s = 0.05</i> 計算的。"

msgid ""
"Proportion of variance in each endogenous variable explained by its "
"predictors in the model. Values range from 0 to 1, with higher values "
"indicating more variance explained."
msgstr ""
"模型中每個內生變項能被其預測變項解釋的變異比例。數值範圍為 0 到 1，數值愈高表"
"示解釋的變異量愈多。"

msgid "Average Variance Extracted"
msgstr "平均變異抽取量 (AVE)"

msgid ""
"Average Variance Extracted (AVE) measures the amount of variance captured by "
"a latent construct relative to measurement error. AVE values above 0.5 "
"indicate adequate convergent validity, meaning the construct explains more "
"than half the variance of its indicators."
msgstr ""
"平均變異萃取量（AVE）用以衡量潛在構念相對於測量誤差所能解釋的變異量。AVE 值大"
"於 0.5 表示具有足夠的收斂效度，即該構念能解釋其指標變項超過一半的變異量。"

msgid "AVE"
msgstr "平均變異抽取量 (AVE)"

msgid "Reliability"
msgstr "信度指標 (Cronbach's α 與 CR值)"

msgid ""
"Composite reliability coefficients for each latent construct. Coefficient α "
"(alpha) assumes tau-equivalence (equal loadings), while coefficient ω "
"(omega) allows for congeneric indicators (unequal loadings) and is generally "
"preferred. Values above 0.7 are commonly considered acceptable."
msgstr ""
"每個潛在構念之組合信度係數。α 係數假設 tau-等效性（負荷量相等），而 ω 係數則"
"允許異質指標（負荷量不相等），通常較受推薦。數值高於 0.7 一般視為可接受。"

msgid "Coefficient α"
msgstr "Coefficient α"

msgid "Coefficient ω"
msgstr "Coefficient ω (CR值)"

msgid "Heterotrait-Monotrait Ratio"
msgstr "異質-單質比"

msgid ""
"Heterotrait-Monotrait (HTMT) ratio of correlations for assessing "
"discriminant validity. HTMT values below 0.85 (conservative) or 0.90 "
"(liberal) suggest that constructs are empirically distinct from each other."
msgstr ""
"用於評估區別效度之異質－同質相關比（HTMT）。HTMT 值低於 0.85（嚴格）或 0.90（"
"寬鬆）表示構念之間在實證上具有區別性。"

msgid "Mardia's Coefficients"
msgstr "Mardia 係數"

msgid ""
"Mardia's multivariate skewness and kurtosis coefficients for assessing "
"whether the data meet the multivariate normality assumption. Significant "
"values suggest non-normality, which may affect chi-square tests and standard "
"errors under ML estimation."
msgstr ""
"用於評估資料是否符合多變量常態性假設之 Mardia 多變量偏度與峰度係數。若數值顯"
"著，表示非常態性存在，可能會影響 ML 估計下之卡方檢定與標準誤。"

msgid "Coefficient"
msgstr "係數"

msgid "z"
msgstr "z"

msgid ""
"Multivariate skewness and kurtosis calculated for observed variables from "
"all models."
msgstr "根據所有模型的觀察變數來計算多變數偏態與峰度。"

msgid ""
"Not all used variables are continuous: Mardia's coefficients not available."
msgstr "因有非數值的變數而無法計算Mardia係數。"

msgid ""
"The data covariance matrix could not be inverted: Mardia's coefficients not "
"available."
msgstr "因有非數值的變數而無法計算Mardia係數。"

msgid "Skewness"
msgstr "偏態"

msgid "Kurtosis"
msgstr "峰度"

msgid "Covariance Tables"
msgstr "共變數表"

msgid ""
"Observed, model-implied, and residual covariance matrices. Comparing these "
"matrices helps evaluate local model fit."
msgstr "觀察、模型隱含與殘差共變數矩陣。比較這些矩陣有助於評估局部模型適配度。"

msgid "Observed Covariance Matrix"
msgstr "觀察共變數矩陣"

msgid ""
"Sample covariance matrix of the observed variables used for model estimation."
msgstr "用於模型估計之觀察變項樣本共變數矩陣。"

msgid ""
"Model-implied covariance matrix derived from the estimated parameters. Close "
"correspondence with the observed covariance matrix indicates good model fit."
msgstr ""
"根據估計參數推導之模型隱含共變數矩陣。此矩陣與觀察共變數矩陣愈接近，表示模型"
"適配度愈好。"

msgid ""
"Difference between the observed and model-implied covariance matrices. Small "
"residuals indicate that the model reproduces the observed covariances well."
msgstr ""
"觀察共變數矩陣與模型隱含共變數矩陣之差異。殘差較小表示模型能夠良好地再現觀察"
"共變數。"

msgid "Standardized Residual Covariance Matrix"
msgstr "標準化殘差共變數矩陣"

msgid ""
"Standardized residual covariances. Values exceeding |2| may indicate "
"localized areas of poor fit for specific pairs of variables."
msgstr "標準化殘差共變數。數值超過 |2| 可能表示特定變項對之間存在局部適配不良之處。"

msgid ""
"The standardized residual covariance table is currently unavailable when the "
"error calculation method is 'Bootstrap'"
msgstr "以拔靴法計算誤差時，無法提供標準化殘差共變數表"

msgid "The standardized residual covariance matrix could not be computed"
msgstr "無法計算標準化殘差共變數矩陣"

msgid ""
"The standardized residual covariance tables are currently unavailable when "
"the error calculation method is 'Bootstrap'"
msgstr "以拔靴法計算誤差時，無法提供標準化殘差共變數表"

msgid "The standardized residual covariance matrices could not be computed"
msgstr "無法計算標準化殘差共變數矩陣"

msgid "Modification Indices"
msgstr "修正指標"

msgid ""
"Modification indices (MI) estimate the expected decrease in the model chi-"
"square statistic if a currently fixed parameter were freed. The expected "
"parameter change (EPC) indicates the approximate value of the freed "
"parameter."
msgstr ""
"修正指標（MI）估計若將當前固定之參數釋放時，模型卡方統計量預期會減少之數值。"
"預期參數變化（EPC）則顯示該釋放參數之近似值。"

msgid ""
"MI is the expected chi-square decrease if a fixed parameter is freed. EPC is "
"the expected parameter change. SEPC columns show standardized versions (lv = "
"latent only, all = fully, nox = excluding exogenous observed)."
msgstr ""
"MI 為釋放一個固定參數時預期之卡方減少值。EPC 為預期之參數變化量。SEPC 欄位顯"
"示標準化版本（lv = 僅潛在變項、all = 完全標準化、nox = 排除外生觀察變項）。"

msgid "MI"
msgstr ""

msgid "EPC"
msgstr ""

msgid "SEPC (lv)"
msgstr ""

msgid "SEPC (all)"
msgstr "SEPC（完全標準化）"

msgid "SEPC (nox)"
msgstr "SEPC（排除外生觀察變項）"

msgid "Sensitivity Analysis"
msgstr "敏感度分析"

msgid ""
"Sensitivity analysis using phantom variables to assess the robustness of "
"path estimates to unmeasured confounding. Evaluates whether conclusions "
"change when an unobserved common cause is introduced."
msgstr ""
"使用虛擬變項進行敏感度分析，以評估路徑估計值對未測量干擾之穩健性。此分析檢驗"
"當引入未觀察到之共同原因時，結論是否會改變。"

msgid "Summary of Sensitivity Analysis"
msgstr "敏感度分析摘要"

msgid ""
"Summary of how path estimates and their significance change when phantom "
"variables representing unmeasured confounders are introduced. P* denotes the "
"p-value from the sensitivity model."
msgstr ""
"當引入代表未測量干擾變項之虛擬變項時，路徑估計值及其顯著性如何變化之摘要。P* "
"代表敏感度模型之 p 值。"

msgid "Path"
msgstr "路徑圖"

msgid "Standardized estimate"
msgstr "標準化估計值"

msgid "Original model"
msgstr "原始模型"

msgid "p*"
msgstr "p*"

msgid "Sensitivity model"
msgstr "敏感度模型"

msgid "Min"
msgstr "最小值"

msgid "Max"
msgstr "最大值"

msgid ""
"Please include at least one regression path in the model to perform a "
"sensitivity analysis."
msgstr "請在模型中包含至少一條迴歸路徑，以進行敏感度分析。"

msgid "Performing sensitivity analysis (model: %1$s, group: %2$s)"
msgstr "進行敏感度分析 (模型: %1$s, 組: %2$s)"

msgid "Performing sensitivity analysis (model: %1$s)"
msgstr "進行敏感度分析 (模型: %1$s)"

msgid "Sensitivity Parameters That Led to a Change in Significance"
msgstr "導致顯著性改變之敏感度參數"

msgid ""
"Phantom variable coefficients from sensitivity models where the statistical "
"significance of a path changed compared to the original model."
msgstr ""
"在敏感度模型中，當某路徑之統計顯著性與原始模型相比發生改變時，所對應之虛擬變"
"項係數。"

msgid "Sensitivity parameters"
msgstr "敏感性參數"

msgid "Summary of Sensitivity Parameters"
msgstr "敏感度參數摘要"

msgid ""
"Summary statistics (mean, min, max) of the phantom variable coefficients "
"across all sensitivity analyses, indicating the range of unmeasured "
"confounding explored."
msgstr ""
"所有敏感度分析中，虛擬變項係數之摘要統計量（平均數、最小值、最大值），用以顯"
"示所探討之未測量干擾範圍。"

msgid "Sensitivity parameter"
msgstr "敏感性參數"

msgid "Path Diagram"
msgstr "路徑圖"

msgid ""
"Graphical representation of the model showing latent variables (circles), "
"observed variables (squares), and the paths between them."
msgstr "模型之圖形呈現，顯示潛在變項（圓形）、觀察變項（方形）以及它們之間的路徑。"

