msgstr "Yuan-Bentler (Mplus) 量尺化檢定統計數"

msgid "mean and variance-adjusted"
msgstr "平均數與變異數調整檢定統計數"

msgid "scaled and shifted"
msgstr "量尺與轉變(shifted)檢定統計數"

